UML:TaggedValue.value: The Portfolio Canvas is a type of Business Model Canvas that has been adapted to charter and describe the structure and purpose of a SAFe portfolio. The portfolio canvas describes how a portfolio of solutions creates, delivers, and captures value for an organization. It also helps define and align the portfolio’s Value Streams and Solutions to the goals of the enterprise.
